```plantuml
@startuml OpenPSD_modelbank

package "Presentation Layer" {
    [ModelBankController] as Controller
    [gRPC Server] as GRPCServer
}

package "Application Layer" {
    [ModelBankUseCase] as UseCase
}

package "Domain Layer" {
    [FinancialInstitution] as FI
    [AccountHolder] as AH
    [Account] as Account
    [Consent] as Consent
    [PaymentInstruction] as Payment
    [LedgerEntry] as Ledger
}

package "Infrastructure Layer" {
    [DbProvider] as DB
    [PostgreSQL] as Postgres
}

Controller --> UseCase : <<uses>>\nvia InputPort
UseCase --> Controller : <<notifies>>\nvia OutputPort

UseCase --> DB : <<uses>>\nvia EntityGateway
DB --> Postgres : <<persists to>>

GRPCServer --> Controller : <<calls>>

FI --* AH
AH --* Account
Account --* Ledger
Payment --* Ledger
Consent -- Account

note right of UseCase: Core business logic\nfor payment processing\nand account management

note bottom of Postgres: Stores all domain entities\nand transaction data

@enduml
```